1
00:00:00,400 --> 00:00:01,880
Alright, time to sleep!

2
00:00:01,880 --> 00:00:03,240
Who would want to sleep with you?

3
00:00:03,240 --> 00:00:04,120
Get out of here.

4
00:00:04,120 --> 00:00:05,360
What's the big deal? We're brothers.

5
00:00:05,720 --> 00:00:06,800
I told you.

6
00:00:06,800 --> 00:00:08,720
Brothers don't sleep in the same bed.

7
00:00:12,600 --> 00:00:13,720
This manga...

8
00:00:13,720 --> 00:00:15,720
It's been lying around in the living room.

9
00:00:18,320 --> 00:00:19,600
Just leave it there.

10
00:00:20,320 --> 00:00:22,800
You're still into this stuff?

11
00:00:24,720 --> 00:00:27,560
Yeah, so what? I like it.

12
00:00:27,560 --> 00:00:28,560
Sorry if it grosses you out.

13
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:30,360
It's not that...

14
00:00:30,360 --> 00:00:32,840
It's good to have things you enjoy.

15
00:00:33,520 --> 00:00:34,520
But...

16
00:00:34,680 --> 00:00:36,640
Given my reputation at school...

17
00:00:39,240 --> 00:00:40,680
Because you're...

18
00:00:40,680 --> 00:00:42,240
The popular guy everyone looks up to?

19
00:00:43,040 --> 00:00:44,440
You're one to talk.

20
00:00:44,440 --> 00:00:46,480
Always acting like such a loner.

21
00:00:46,480 --> 00:00:49,480
I just don't see the point in socializing.

22
00:00:50,120 --> 00:00:51,320
I envy you.

23
00:00:51,920 --> 00:00:54,440
I have to hide my true self at school.

24
00:00:56,320 --> 00:00:57,840
We're brothers.

25
00:00:57,840 --> 00:00:59,720
There's no need to hide anything here.

26
00:01:02,240 --> 00:01:04,160
Shut up...

27
00:01:04,160 --> 00:01:04,840
Whew...

28
00:01:04,840 --> 00:01:05,840
Bathroom, bathroom...

29
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:23,160
Sorry...

30
00:01:24,080 --> 00:01:25,840
Who are you apologizing to?
